eventState.description: The curent event state. Can be NOT_STARTED,WAR_WARMUP,WAR_RUNNING,WAR_GRACE_PERIOD,WAR_FINISHED

rewardState.description: After a war, you can check if rewards have been given out. Can be TOO_EARLY,PROCESSING,FINISHED

tier.description: The guild's tier in this event

nextMatchEpoch.description: Unix epoch timestamp. This is when the daily matches will reset

groupGuildLeaderboard.description: An array of guild scores for all the guilds in this group

memberContributionsLeaderboard.description: An array of scores. This represents the medallions won be each player in the current guild. This can include members not currently in the guild if they won a match but left during the event
